    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Throwable>

    public class ConnectionSetupException
extends java.sql.SQLException
    An exception class that is used to denote error condition during connection setup. A possible action is to wait (sleep) and retry.
    Version:
    1.0
